snippet.title: 《Game Theory At Christmas》Trailers
snippet.description:
In order to participate in the game competition, let's make a game with the theme of Game Theory. Originally thought so, but due to various complicated reasons. In the end it became a spoof game.

BGM source：甘茶の音楽工房、tan90
Download link：https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DefaultCom.GameTheoryAtChristmas&hl=es_SV&gl=US
